  "prompt": "Some people believe that juveniles who commit crimes should be treated the same way as adults, while others feel there are better alternatives. Discuss both views and give your opinion.",
  "prompt_jp": "罪を犯した少年の扱いについて、更生を重視する立場と自分の意見を述べよ。",
  "outline_jp": [
    "対比: 一方で投獄すべきでないとの意見",
    "手段: 社会奉仕で更生させる",
    "理由: 刑務所で悪い犯罪行動を学ぶ",
    "自分の意見: 重罪には甘すぎるが多くは更生が適する"
  ],
  "model_answer": [
    "On the other hand, many people believe that juveniles should not be put in jail like adults.",
    "Instead, offenders can be rehabilitated by doing community service.",
    "This is because young people may learn even worse criminal behaviour from hardened criminals in prison.",
    "For instance, lending a hand in the community teaches useful life skills.",
    "In my view, a slap on the wrist is not enough for serious crimes, but rehabilitation suits most young offenders."
  ],
